script.code:
import com.evolveum.midpoint.prism.query.* import com.evolveum.midpoint.prism.path.* import com.evolveum.midpoint.xml.ns._public.common.common_3.* import com.evolveum.midpoint.xml.ns._public.common.common_3.AssignmentType import com.evolveum.midpoint.xml.ns._public.common.common_3.ObjectReferenceType import com.evolveum.midpoint.xml.ns._public.common.common_3.OrgType import javax.xml.namespace.QName import java.util.*
if(!input) return
parts = input.split(":") id_org_whois = parts[0] souvislost = Integer.valueOf(parts[1]) funkce = parts.size() > 2 ? (parts[2]?.split(",")?.collect({ Integer.valueOf(it).toBigInteger() }) ?: []) : []
// log.info("XXX hrana org {} souvislost {} funkce {}", id_org_whois, souvislost, funkce)
def mapSouvislost = [ 0 : "system", 1 : "zamestnavatel", 2 : "pracoviste", 3 : "fakulta", 4 : "fakulta_dalsi_obor", 5 : "studium", 6 : "clen", 7 : "externista", 8 : "vyucujici", 9 : "uzivatel", 10 : "samosprava", 20 : "prvouk_hlavni", 21 : "prvouk_vztah", 40 : "ucastnik_habilitace", 50 : "agenda" ]
relation = mapSouvislost[souvislost] ?: "souvislost"
prismContext = midpoint.getPrismContext() query = prismContext.queryFor(OrgType.class) .item("identifier").eq(id_org_whois) .build()
objects = midpoint.searchObjects(OrgType.class, query) org = objects && !objects.isEmpty() ? objects.first() : null //log.info("XXX org {}" , org)
if(org == null) { return null }
orgOrt = new ObjectReferenceType() orgOrt.setOid(org.getOid()) orgOrt.setType(OrgType.COMPLEX_TYPE) orgOrt.setRelation(new QName("http://cas.cuni.cz/idm/relation", relation))
assignment = new AssignmentType()
relationQName = new QName("http://midpoint.cuni.cz/xml/ns/cas", "relation") functionsQName = new QName("http://midpoint.cuni.cz/xml/ns/cas", "functions")
ext_pcv = assignment.asPrismContainerValue().findOrCreateContainer(AssignmentType.F_EXTENSION) // log.info("XXX PCV {}", ext_pcv) ext_pcv?.findOrCreateProperty(ItemName.fromQName(relationQName))?.addRealValue(souvislost.toBigInteger()) for (f in funkce) { ext_pcv?.findOrCreateProperty(ItemName.fromQName(functionsQName))?.addRealValue(f) }
return assignment .subtype("relation_hrana") .subtype("hrana_" + basic.getIdentifierValue(shadow)) .targetRef(orgOrt)
